Middleware
-> inspecting and filtering HTTP requests
-> pa make:middleware command
-> Middleware & Responses : A middleware can perform tasks before or after passing the request
-> Registering Middleware
    - Global Middleware : $middleware property of your app/Http/Kernel.php class
    - Assigning Middleware To Routes : $routeMiddleware property of ... with key
    - Excluding Middleware : withoutMiddleware(middleware name OR class)
    - Middleware Groups : $middlewareGroups property of ... with group name
-> Sorting Middleware : Rarely, $middlewarePriority property
-> Middleware Parameters
-> Terminable Middleware : 
    - When you need to do some work after the response has been sent to browser
    - terminate() method : will automatically be called after the response is sent to the browser